Introduction

Youngeun is a South Korean singer, dancer and rapper under Biscuit Entertainment.

In 2021, Youngeun participated in the MNET survival show Girls Planet 999 where she finished 5th place, securing her spot as a member of the South Korean project girl group Kep1er.

Youngeun debuted as a member of Kep1er on January 3, 2022, with their first mini-album "First Impact" and the title track "WA DA DA."
